@host = http://localhost:5298
@token = REPLACE_AFTER_LOGIN

### Health
GET {{host}}/api/health

### MongoDB test (database: ubaxsana)
GET {{host}}/api/health/mongodb

### Count saved documents (xogta database-ka)
GET {{host}}/api/health/data

### Login
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@assisted.local",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Active delivery zones (public)
GET {{host}}/api/delivery/zones/active

### Create order (public)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Ahmed Ali",
  "phone": "+252612345678",
  "productUrl": "https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/example",
  "quantity": 1,
  "districtId": "ZONE-HODAN",
  "addressDetail": "Near Bakara market"
}

### Admin — list orders
GET {{host}}/api/orders?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard analytics
GET {{host}}/api/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
